{
  "id": "adv_main_02_13_01",
  "title": "東京編2章36話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 4.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、お疲れ様です！\nカメラ、返しに来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san‚ good work!\nI came to return the camera.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様……その様子だとインタビューをした甲斐は\nあったみたいだな。答え、見つかったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work… From the looks of it‚ the interviews seem to have\nbeen worthwhile. Did you find your answer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nというか……最初から、私達の中にあったみたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nOr rather… it seems like it was inside us all along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、そうだったのか\n聞かせてくれないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ is that so?\nTell me about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "勝ち負けにこだわらないで、全力でステージを楽しむ\nそれが、私達サニーピースの強みでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not dwelling on winning or losing‚ and enjoying the stage with all our might.\nThat was Sunny Peace's strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "でもそれは、自分達が楽しむだけではない……\nましてや、ファンを楽しませるだけでもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not just about us enjoying ourselves…\nAnd it's not just about entertaining the fans either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ファンの想いを受け止めて、歌に込めて返す……\nそしてまた、届いた想いを受け止めて、歌に込める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Receiving the fans' feelings and putting them into our songs…\nAnd then receiving those feelings again and putting them into our songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって私達五つのピースとお客さん一人一人の\nピースを集め、絆に変えてどんどん広げていく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how we gather the five pieces of ourselves and the pieces of each and every fan‚\nturn them into bonds‚ and spread them further and further.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それが、私達にとってのアイドルで――\nアイドルとして成し遂げたいこと、なんだと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's what idols are to us‚ and--\nI think that's what we want to achieve as idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "それが……答え……\nさくら達は……見つかったんだね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… the answer…\nSakura and the others… you found it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 86.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ファンと自分達との、絆の輪……か\n確かに、ステージを楽しむからこそ、出来ることだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A circle of bonds… between the fans and yourselves‚ huh?\nCertainly‚ it's something you can do because you enjoy the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（そして、その答えに自分達の力で辿り着けた、か）\n（……凄いな、みんな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And they were able to arrive at that answer on their own.)\n(…You guys are amazing…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？\nなんだか、妙に感慨にふけっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong?\nYou seem lost in thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、すみません。ちょっと考え事をしてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry. I was just thinking about something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それで{user}さん、実は……\n一生に一度のお願いがあるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Manager-san‚ actually…\nI have a once-in-a-lifetime favor to ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "遠慮しないで言ってくれ\n俺に出来ることならなんでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't hesitate to ask.\nAnything I can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 126.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 126.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 126.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "新曲に、新衣装……！？\nしかも、ファイナルまでにって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new song‚ new costumes…!?\nAnd by the finals…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今の私達の想いを、言葉だけじゃなくて\nちゃんと形にして見せたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I want to show our current feelings not just through words‚\nbut in a tangible form.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 139.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで話し合ってたら、イメージが膨らんで……\n絶対、新曲と新衣装がほしいよね、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were talking about it‚ and the image grew…\nWe definitely want a new song and new costumes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それを、今から作り始めて\nファイナルまでに完成させる、っていうのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want to start making them now\nand finish them by the finals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 154.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あのう……や、やっぱり、無理でしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… i-is that really impossible…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃそうだよ……\nファイナルまであと二週間しかないんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it is…\nThere are only two weeks left until the finals!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 164.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今の私達が全力を出し尽くしても\nそれだけじゃ勝てない。それくらい実力差があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But even if we give it our all‚\nthat's not enough to win. The skill gap is that big.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 174.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君の力で\nなんとかならないかなぁ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't you do something about it\nwith your power‚ Manager-kun～?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 177.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "佐伯遙子、一生のお願い！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko Saeki's once-in-a-lifetime favor!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 181.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_13_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……時間がなさ過ぎるわ\n本番までに仕上げられなかったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… there's not enough time.\nIf we can't finish it by the performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 188.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
